                    <p><span>Where we rely on our legitimate interest</span></p>
                    <p>In cases where we are processing your personal data on the basis of our legitimate interest, you can ask us to stop for reasons connected to your individual situation.</p>
                    <p>We must then do so, unless we believe we have a legitimate overriding reason to continue processing your personal data. If we choose not to action your request, we'll explain the reasons for our refusal.</p>
                    <p><span><strong>Checking your identity</strong></span></p>
